<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>TimeAuction || About Us</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Oleo+Script|PT Sans Narrow|Open+Sans:400,300|Open+Sans+Condensed:300' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>

  <%= render 'partials/nav' %>

  <div id="flash">
    <% flash.each do |name, msg| %>
      <%= content_tag :div, msg, :id => "flash_#{name}", class: "alert alert-#{name}" %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="aboutImage">
    <div class="aboutBoxContent">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p>TimeAuction evangelizes volunteership by giving eager participants another great reason to perform charity work.</p>
      <p>David Wen started TimeAuction in 2007 as a part-time gift back to the community. Now, the message spreads online.</p>
      <p>Also worth noting, this current version of the TimeAuction website is the final Dev Bootcamp project of the 4 handsome gentlemen you see below.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="aboutBox">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="splashContainer">
    <h2>The TimeAuction Developers</h2>
    <div class="row">

      <div class="span3">
        <div class="teamCell">
          <div class="teamImage">
            <%= cl_image_tag('v1365986316/d_kndyme.jpg', :width => 250, :height => 250) %>
          </div>
          <h4>David Wen</h4>
          <div id="location">Vancouver <%= image_tag '/assets/CA.png' %></div>
          <p>David is the Founder of the original TimeAuction.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="span3">
        <div class="teamCell">
          <div class="teamImage">
            <%= cl_image_tag('v1365986316/k_z3rxfw.jpg', :width => 250, :height => 250) %>
          </div>
          <h4>Kevin Ko</h4>
          <div id="location">Los Angeles <%= image_tag '/assets/us.png' %></div>
          <p>Kevin is a full-stack engineer with a passion for visual design. He built the front-end design, including CSS, HTML, and AJAX comment submission.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="span3">
        <div class="teamCell">
          <div class="teamImage">
            <%= cl_image_tag('v1365986316/p_hlfngk.jpg', :width => 250, :height => 250) %>
            </div>
          <h4>Philip Woo</h4>
          <div id="location">Seoul <%= image_tag '/assets/KR.png' %></div>
          <p>Philip is a</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="span3">
        <div class="teamCell">
          <div class="teamImage">
            <%= cl_image_tag('v1365986316/j_v3ndox.jpg', :width => 250, :height => 250) %>
          </div>
          <h4>J Connolly</h4>
          <div id="location">Los Angeles <%= image_tag '/assets/us.png' %></div>
          <p>J is a rails developer and founder of LiftHero.com, which aims to make arranging transportation for seniors seamless and affordable. He delivers groceries as a volunteer for Meals on Wheels San Francisco.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="aboutGithub">
      <%= link_to image_tag('/assets/github-icon.png'), 'https://www.github.com/Dawenster/time_auction' %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= render 'partials/footer' %>
</body>
</html>
